data.description:
Back on the market due to no fault of the seller.  Buyer could not get financing. 
Their loss is your gain!  Beautifully maintained 3 bed, 2 bath, 1586 sq.ft. brick ranch with full unfinished walkout basement and 2 car attached garage on 1.0 acre nicely landscaped lot.  Large, covered patio in back is accessed from kitchen nook through large sliding glass door.  Freshly painted interior with newer floorcoverings throughout.  Andersen windows, heat pump, wood burning stove and fireplace, paved driveway, public water and well, septic.  Nice mini barn in back for lawn tools. This home has it all and is move-in ready.  Located minutes from  Kingsport, Duffield, and Big Stone Gap.
